		"§7Crimsite is a Create stone resource discovered while exploring and mining.§r"
		" "
		"§fGather 16 Crimsite to prepare the custom core tied to Iron generation.§r"
		" "
		"§eThis part is intentionally exploration-first: find the resource, then automate the metal.§r"
